23
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,840
Bekalan makanan Yanbei pula cukup,

24
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:48,360
ia cukup untuk 50 ribu Tentera
Burung Layang-layang serang ke arah timur.

25
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,000
Tuanku,

26
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:51,030
