30
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,030
Awak...

31
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,310
Mari sini.

32
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:25,840
Tuanku.

33
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,490
Angkat kepala awak.

34
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,130
Awak persembahkan tarian apa?

35
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,030
Inilah tarian perang Yanbei.

36
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,079
Inilah tarian yang memuji
semangat pahlawan Yanbei

37
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:40,210
yang tak takut musuh kuat,
meluaskan wilayah

38
00:03:40,210 --> 00:03:41,490
serta melawan langit dan bumi ini.

39
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:43,520
Meluaskan wilayah?

40
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,680
Melawan langit dan bumi ini?

41
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:48,630
Bagus!

42
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,880
Kurniakan ganjaran kepada dia!

43
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,630
Kenapa awak menghalang saya tadi?

44
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,000
Saya bergegas ke sini dengan melalui
beratus-ratus batu perjalanan semalaman

45
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,560
adalah untuk mendapat jawapan baginda!

46
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,220
Kenapa awak menghalang saya?

47
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:19,480
Awak tak nampak baginda
asyik pandang penari itu

48
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:21,920
