51
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:28,860
Sudahlah.

52
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:09,240
[REBIRTH]

53
00:06:09,730 --> 00:06:12,230
[Episod 10]

54
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:26,830
Teh.

55
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,159
Tuanku.

56
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,450
Kenapa awak berada di sini?

57
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,420
Patik datang untuk layan tuanku.

58
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:59,050
Haraplah tuanku jangan salahkan
patik yang cuai dan dungu.

59
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,460
Awak daripada puak yang mana?

60
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,860
Sembah malum, tuanku.

61
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,060
Patik daripada Puak Pale.

62
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,600
Puak Pale?

63
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,700
Layanlah beta tukar baju.

64
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:43,920
Baju dan barang kemas
yang awak pakai sangat berharga.

65
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:47,480
Adakah Ketua Puak Pale yang
memberikan semua ini kepada awak

66
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,880
dan suruh awak datang untuk menggoda beta?

67
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,240
Tuanku, jangan bergurau.

68
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:56,460
Ketua Puak Pale ialah
bapa saudara kepada patik.

69
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,970
Semasa patik masih kecil,

70
00:07:58,290 --> 00:08:01,220
