di kediaman pak cik patik.

71
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,920
Patik suka tuanku sehingga sekarang.

72
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,040
Tuanku.

73
00:08:18,930 --> 00:08:19,580
Tuanku.

74
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,490
Beritahulah pak cik awak yang angkuh itu.

75
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:36,440
Jika dia cuba
berlagak pandai lagi lain kali,

76
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,390
awak

77
00:08:38,530 --> 00:08:41,440
