83
00:08:58,770 --> 00:08:59,730
Penari?

84
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:04,630
Dia anak saudara perempuan kandung
kepada si tua daripada Puak Pale!

85
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:06,150
Mereka tak sabar-sabar untuk

86
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:07,720
