90
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:16,870
Tuanku,

91
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,320
ampunkan patik kerana berterus terang.

92
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,600
Sepanjang tempoh masa ini,

93
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:23,480
