94
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,840
Memberontak?

95
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:33,410
Beta juga tahu biarpun
awak tak sembah maklum beta.

96
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,960
Mereka pastilah bertitah sebegini,

97
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,790
Maharaja Yan tiada maharani dan keturunan.

98
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,550
Belum tentu lagi bahawa Yanbei

99
