102
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,200
Tak berani?

103
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,360
Chu.

104
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,440
Di Yanbei,

105
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:29,510
hanya orang yang mampu
mengawal helang hitam ini,

106
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,720
barulah dia layak jadi Maharaja Yanbei.

107
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,200
Mari.

108
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:47,290
Chu,

109
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,600
