110
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:54,600
Siapa mahu jadi maharani awak?

111
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,550
Saya tak mahu.

112
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:58,450
Saya tak tipu awak,

113
00:10:58,650 --> 00:10:59,550
