kawasan sempadan Biantang.

135
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:43,250
Setelah masuk ke Biantang,
awak mesti perhatikan dia baik-baik.

136
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:44,800
Sebaik sahaja dia ada sebarang tindakan,

137
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:45,940
beritahulah saya segera,

138
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:48,270
jangan biarkan sebarang masalah timbul.

139
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,070
Ya.

140
00:12:48,890 --> 00:12:51,070
[Ba Ze, pahlawan Puak Lingyue]

141
