143
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:44,300
Awak benar-benar ditakutkan?

144
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,320
Dia bukan Maharaja Ximeng.

145
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,150
Apa?

146
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:08,240
Beta menggunakan adat Ximeng

147
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,870
