173
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,310
Beta bukannya tak mahu tanggalkan topeng,

174
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:44,460
tapi wajah beta pelik

175
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:45,840
dan sangat menakutkan.

176
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,070
Dalam jamuan negara,

177
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,440
jika beta tanggalkan topeng,

178
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,630
ia akan jadi tak sopan pula.

179
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:53,670
Maharaja Ximeng
menggunakan adat negara Ximeng

180
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:55,550
ketika menghadap baginda tadi.

181
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:57,670
Ketika santap arak sekarang,

182
00:15:57,670 --> 00:16:00,220
Maharaja Ximeng pula
tak sudi tanggalkan topeng.

183
00:16:00,220 --> 00:16:03,480
Maharaja Ximeng begitu
tak sudi ikut adat negara Biantang

184
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:07,000
kerana Biantang ialah
negara kecil di Dataran Tengah

185
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,630
dan tak seluas Ximeng,

186
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:12,080
Maharaja Ximeng pun tak sudi menghormati

187
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,120
baginda dan beta?

188
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:16,480
Kenapa Yang Teramat Mulia
mesti menyusahkan beta?

189
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:19,870
Jika Maharaja Ximeng tak sudi
menanggalkan topeng sendiri,

190
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:23,390
beta akan menitahkan seseorang
untuk membantu Maharaja Ximeng.

191
00:16:23,390 --> 00:16:26,250
Awak pergilah tanggalkan
topeng Maharaja Ximeng.

192
00:16:32,430 --> 00:16:33,550
Tak guna!

193
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:35,750
Berani awak biadab
terhadap Maharaja Ximeng!

194
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:36,750
Heret dia keluar!

195
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:37,630
Pukul dia sampai mati.

196
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:39,690
Yang Teramat Mulia, ampunkan patik!

197
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:41,180
Patik dah tahu bersalah!

198
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:43,320
Yang Teramat Mulia, ampunkan patik!

199
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,530
Yang Teramat Mulia, ampunkan patik!

200
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:46,590
Yang Teramat Mulia, ampunkan patik!

201
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,150
Awak pergi.

202
00:16:55,010 --> 00:16:57,070
Yang Teramat Mulia, ampunkan patik!

203
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,720
Patik dah tahu bersalah!

204
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:01,910
Beta rasa biarpun
mereka yang mencerobohi Biantang,

205
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:05,720
merogol wanita dan merompak harta
di kawasan sempadan selama ini

206
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:07,160
berasal dari Ximeng,

207
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,640
namun mereka pastilah beberapa

208
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:11,109
puak liar yang kurang ajar.

209
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,290
Maharaja Ximeng ada status yang mulia,

210
00:17:13,290 --> 00:17:16,220
Maharaja Ximeng pasti bukan
orang yang begitu kejam

211
00:17:16,349 --> 00:17:17,720
dan takkan tengok
orang yang tak berdosa dibunuh

212
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,920
tanpa buat apa-apa.

213
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,920
Yang Teramat Mulia,

214
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:32,500
ampunkan patik kerana berterus terang.

215
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:34,760
Maharaja Ximeng berstatus mulia.

216
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:37,000
Yang Teramat Mulia menitahkan
dayang-dayang menanggalkan topeng baginda,

217
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:38,510
rasanya perbuatan ini kurang elok.

218
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:40,270
Apa kata biarkan putera mahkota

219
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:42,750
sendiri tengok
wajah sebenar Maharaja Ximeng,

220
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,440
bagaimana?

221
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,110
Fu,

222
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,430
awak sedang buat apa?

223
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:48,430
Beta tak faham.

224
00:17:49,010 --> 00:17:50,620
Apa niat Puteri Fu?

225
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,650
Maharaja Ximeng
berangkat datang ke sini dari jauh

226
00:17:53,650 --> 00:17:55,110
untuk menjalin
hubungan diplomatik dengan Biantang.

227
00:17:55,110 --> 00:17:56,790
Rasanya baginda bukan
tak menghormati Biantang,

228
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:58,310
